<section id="about" class="py-16 border-t" style="border-color: var(--border);">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 reveal" style="color: var(--text);">About</h2>

    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12 leading-relaxed reveal reveal-delay-1" style="color: var(--text-muted);">
      <p>
        I'm Sean, a web developer based in Melbourne. For eight years I ran Level Design, designing bespoke timber tables for architects and private clients. That design discipline—understanding the problem, sketching solutions, not using templates—now shapes how I build web applications.
      </p>
      <p>
        I work across the full stack: React, Next.js, Astro, Supabase day to day. Figma to think through structure before code. I care about shipping clean work over shipping fast.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t pt-8 reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-color: var(--border);">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase font-medium mb-6" style="letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--text-muted);">Credentials</p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
          <p class="font-medium" style="color: var(--text);">Diploma in Back End Web Development</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
          <p class="font-medium" style="color: var(--text);">Cert IV in Web Development</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">→</span>
          <p class="font-medium" style="color: var(--text);">Level Design (ongoing)</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
